# Smoke-replay artifacts. The run-smokes.sh scripts ARE tracked (see explicit
# negation) — they're test infrastructure. Everything else under artifacts/
# is generated output (binaries, captured stdout/stderr/exit codes, fixture
# trees that can exceed Windows MAX_PATH and break git status).
